OL,3,CFather pays tribute after boys killed
OL,4,Cwhen car driven by their mother crashed
OL,6,FThe father of two boys killed when a
OL,7,Fcar driven by their mother crashed in
OL,8,FLincolnshire has paid tribute to them.
OL,10,FEight-year-old Louie Ellis and his six-
OL,11,Fyear-old brother Mason Ellis were in a
OL,12,FVauxhall Astra which crashed with an
OL,13,FAudi car on the A52 between Sandilands
OL,14,Fand Huttoft, near Sutton on Sea,
OL,15,FLincolnshire in October 2023.
OL,17,FLouie died at the scene, Mason died in
OL,18,Fhospital. Their four-year-old brother
OL,19,Fwas also injured but survived. Two
OL,20,Fpeople in an Audi were also injured in
OL,21,Fthe incident.
