OL,4,Cwhen car driven by their mother crashed
OL,6,FTheir mother Amy Sheppard admitted
OL,7,Fcausing death and serious injury by
OL,8,Fcareless driving.
OL,10,FIn December last year she was spared
OL,11,Fjail and given a 20-month suspended
OL,12,Fprison sentence alongside a ban from
OL,13,Fdriving for two years.
OL,15,FLincoln Crown Court heard Sheppard,
OL,16,Ffrom Huttoft, had picked her two sons
OL,17,Fup from primary school in Mablethorpe
OL,18,Fafter finishing her job as a nursery
OL,19,Fnurse when the crash happened.
