OL,6,FJudge James House KC told Lincoln
OL,7,FCrown Court the sentence was "an act
OL,8,Fof mercy". He added, "Her carelessness
OL,9,Fcaused the death of her two sons. It
OL,10,Fhas long been recognised there are
OL,11,Fexceptional cases which come before
OL,12,Fthe courts."
OL,14,FIn a tribute posted by Lincolnshire
OL,15,FPolice, Louie and Mason's father
OL,16,Fcalled them "two extraordinary boys
OL,17,Fwhose love, laughter, and spirit
OL,18,Ffilled every space they were in."
