OL,4,Cwhen car driven by their mother crashed
OL,6,FDescribing a love of football and
OL,7,FLiverpool FC, he said: "Louie had a
OL,8,Fheart full of joy and determination.
OL,9,FHe loved nothing more than playing
OL,10,Ffootball every weekend with his dad
OL,11,Fand uncle, always eager to practise
OL,12,Fand push himself to get better.
OL,14,F"He also loved sitting with his dad
OL,15,Fwatching Liverpool, cheering them on
OL,16,Fwith pride and excitement. The park
OL,17,Fwas one of his happiest places, where
OL,18,Fhis energy and love for the game truly
OL,19,Fshone."
