OL,6,FOn younger brother Mason, he said:
OL,7,F"Mason's world was fuelled by
OL,8,Fimagination and creativity. He loved
OL,9,FMario and would turn everyday moments
OL,10,Finto adventures.
OL,12,F"Mason also loved spending quiet,
OL,13,Fspecial moments with his grandad,
OL,14,Fsitting on his knee in the garage
OL,15,Fwhile his grandad made wooden toys."
