OL,6,FFather Laurie spoke of family days
OL,7,Fout. He said: "One of the weekends
OL,8,Fboth Louie and Mason absolutely loved
OL,9,Fwas when the slip and slide came out
OL,10,Fwith the paddling pool. That day was
OL,11,Ffilled with squeals of laughter,
OL,12,Fsplashing water and pure happiness.
OL,14,FLaurie also spoke of the boys' impact
OL,15,Fon their younger brother. He said:
OL,16,F"They were the very best big brothers.
OL,17,FProtective, caring and endlessly proud
OL,18,Fof him.
