OL,3,CFather pays tribute after boys killed
OL,4,Cwhen car driven by their mother crashed
OL,6,F"Louie and Mason had the most
OL,7,Fbeautiful souls. Their kindness,
OL,8,Fwarmth, and laughter drew people to
OL,9,Fthem, and everyone who knew them
OL,10,Fadored them.
OL,12,F"I now find myself counting down the
OL,13,Fdays until I am reunited with my Louie
OL,14,Fand Mason. Knowing that they will be
OL,15,Fwaiting for me at the end of my days
OL,16,Fbrings me comfort and peace, and it
OL,17,Ftakes away any fear of passing away.
OL,19,F"Louie and Mason will always be deeply
OL,20,Floved, forever missed, and never
OL,21,Fforgotten."
